  }))), "Causal Analysis and Resolution"), mdx("p", null, "Through the whole interview process, the participants occasionally compared the design-system-driven workflow with the traditional one. The newly opened opportunities such as live prototyping and lean resource management (themes \u201CEnsured design implementation\u201D and \u201CIncreased reliability\u201D) demonstrate the characteristics of CAR. In other words, the causes of the workflow improvements have been understood and analyzed on the sub-processes level."), mdx("p", null, "The interviewees expressed their positive attitude towards using design systems and mentioned that this has been discussed in their companies and teams."), mdx("h5", {
